&lt;p&gt;You could make &lt;strong&gt;a function that will work for any of the &lt;code&gt;word&lt;/code&gt; elements&lt;/strong&gt; and pass in the number of the one you want to transform, like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;snippet&quot; data-lang=&quot;js&quot; data-hide=&quot;false&quot; data-console=&quot;true&quot; data-babel=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
